h1>
<p>API upload and download api profiling<br>
  -------------------------------------------------------</p>
<p><u>Setup details </u></p>
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Name: MacBook Pro<br>
  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Model Identifier: MacBookPro16,2<br>
  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Processor Name: Quad-Core Intel Core i7<br>
  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Processor Speed: 2.3 GHz<br>
  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Number of Processors: 1<br>
  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Total Number of Cores: 4<br>
  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; L2 Cache (per Core): 512 KB<br>
  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; L3 Cache: 8 MB<br>
  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Hyper-Threading Technology: Enabled<br>
  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Memory: 16 GB</p>
