<p><u><strong>JVM server configurations</strong></u></p>
<p>Application server : spring boot undertow</p>
<p>JVM args : -Xms256m -Xmx512m -XX:MaxMetaspaceSize=3D256m -XX:+PrintGCDet=
ails -XX:+PrintGCDateStamps -XX:GCLogFileSize=3D10M<br>
  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -XX:+HeapDumpOnOutOfMemoryError</p>
