<p>Initially, wait for 120 seconds after starting the API server. Then, cal=
l the download API five times for files of a certain file size, with a 10-s=
econd wait between each call. Afterward, pause for 60 seconds. Finally, exe=
cute the upload API five times, waiting 10 seconds between each invocation.=
</p>
